bp?t=1648930041\" width=530 height=32 /></span><br>Your people use the knowledge you gain on each island to enable you to research new technologies and ways of improving your settlements, unlocking tons of new buildings. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/665560/extras/863eb62a0c2a7bc037c5800b3bd0d461.webp?t=1648930041\" width=530 height=32 /></span><br>Dare to take on omens for greater rewards in the future, but risking dangerous curses now!",
